data.description: Step into the timeless allure of a home built in 1925, blended with modern upgrades for today’s discerning homeowner. Outdoor enthusiasts will also appreciate the proximity to scenic parks and trails, showcasing the beauty of Colorado nature.    Nestled in a vibrant community, this home sits just minutes away from downtown Colorado Springs. Living here places you at the epicenter of all that Colorado Springs has to offer, while providing the perfect blend of residential tranquility and city excitement. Cultural events, popular dining spots, and vibrant shopping areas are just a stone's throw away, ensuring you'll never miss out on the local festivities and conveniences.    Practicality is also at the forefront of this property. Recent enhancements ensure you're making a smart choice for long-term living. No worries about the Colorado cold as the furnace was replaced in 2021. Stay comfortable year-round with an air conditioning system installed just a year ago, in 2022. Peace of mind is also part of the package: a new water heater from 2020 for consistent hot showers, and the included radon mitigation system for a healthier living environment for you and your loved ones.    This is not just a house; it's a piece of Colorado Springs history with all the comforts of the modern age. Secure a lifestyle that combines the best of the past and the present with this wonderful opportunity to own a piece of Colorado Springs charm in an unbeatable location! Make it yours today!
